5. Controlled Vocabularies

5.1 Tissues

Each tissue entry is tied to a specific kingdom for biological consistency.

Field	Description

name	Tissue or organ type (e.g., Leaf, Root, Muscle)
kingdom	Biological kingdom (Plant, Animal, etc.)
ontology_id	Reference ontology term (e.g., PO:0009046)


Example:

curl "https://omics.reslab.dev/api/tissues/?kingdom=Plant"


